Pseudocode 

Question 1: 

Start  
Input num1 
Input num2 
Input num3 
IF num1 < num2 and num1< num3 
     Print “num1 is the smallest” 
ELSE IF num2 < num1 and num2 < num3 
     Print “num2 is the smallest “ 
ELSE 
     Print “num3 is the smallest” 
END  


Questions 3: 
Start 
Input num1 
Input num2 
Set result = 0 
Print “Enter ‘*’ for Multiplication or input ‘/’ for Division" 
Input operator 
IF operator == ‘* ‘ 
  result = num1*num2 
ELSE IF operator == ‘/’  
  result = num1/num2  
ELSE  
  Print “Invalid selection” 
Print result 
End 
